turns.content: Can you draw ascii art for a car?
Can you show the car from the side?

Certainly! Here is an ASCII art of a car from the side:
```
   ________
  /        \
 /          \
/            \
|            |
|            |
|            |
|            |
 \          /
  \________/
```
Can you add an arrow pointing to its wheel?

Certainly! Here is an ASCII art of a car with an arrow pointing to one of its wheels:
```
   ________
  /        \
 /          \
/            \
|            |
|            |
|            |
|            |
 \          /
  \________/
       |
       v
  ________
 /        \
/          \
|          |
 \        /
  \______/
```
Can you draw an ascii art of a flower?

Certainly! Here is an ASCII art of a flower:
```
   /\
  /  \
 /    \
 \    /
  \  /
   \/
```
